Introduction by Evenhost1 (Joan):

Welcome everyone to this special event with Zahari (Zaxxon).  
Zahari (Zaxxon) is a 42 year old, former Bulgarian national.  He has been playing bridge for more than 20 years
Zahari has been national champion a few times in all categories . (pairs, teams and mixed pair)   
In 2013 his mixed pairs team won the bronze medal at the 6th European Open Bridge Championships (EOBC) in Oostende.
He is also married and has two sons, 15 and 16 years old - future bridge champions!
@H Welcome back to the BILies Retreat Zahari @h|
